Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.63,0:01:38.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ura! Vacanță, vacanță!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.29,0:01:39.50,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Lily, nu suntem aici ca să ne distrăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Asta e o oportunitate de învățare pentru noi toți.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, te rog. Nu vom învăța nimic în timp ce ne distrăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.92,0:01:51.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ești angajatul nostru de o lună. De unde știi că se va întâmpla una ca asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.75,0:01:55.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Am fost în multe călătorii de „oportunitate de învățare prin muncă”
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,și toate au sfârșit prin a deveni vacanțe.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.29,0:02:00.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu va fi cu nimic diferit nici de această dată.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.29,0:02:05.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,De asta te-am angajat, Leo. Experiența ta este neprețuită.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dar oare mai poți afirma acest lucru după ce vezi asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,E o dărăpănătură!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Doamne.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.13,0:02:21.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Îmi place acest loc! Are un caracter aparte!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes, tu ai ales acest loc, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.71,0:02:30.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Da. Are patru pereți, un acoperiș și e pustiu. E locul perfect.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Așa{\i0} alegi tu locul unde te cazezi?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu văd nimic în neregulă cu asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.58,0:02:40.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dacă oamenii ar afla că liderii Armatei Demonilor s-au adunat aici, s-ar panica.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,E important să rămânem discreți pe toată durata călătoriei.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.46,0:02:52.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Asta are sens. Nimeni nu va știi cine suntem la acest han pustiu.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.63,0:02:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,În plus, i-am spus lui Shutina să ne facă rezervarea sub nume false.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ți-am spus, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.25,0:03:08.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bun-venit, mari lideri ai Armatei Demonilor!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Și s-a zis și cu acoperirea noastră!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare foarte rău!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.58,0:03:12.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Doamne!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, haide, e în reuglă!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.17,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Mulțumim că ne-ați primit!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ne bucurăm să vă avem drept oaspeți.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.63,0:03:23.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Avem un izvor termal în aer liber pe care vi-l recomandăm cu căldură să-l încercați.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.46,0:03:26.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O baie în aer liber! Asta sună grozav.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu avem izvoare termale la castel.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.50,0:03:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cred că mi-ar prinde bine o baie caldă lângă o bere rece.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.58,0:03:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hei, ce este un „izvor termal”? Este asemănător cu o baie?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Da, dar mult mai mare.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pot înota în el?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.88,0:03:41.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,De ce nu?! Vreau să înot!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Haideți să ne concentrăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Suntem aici pentru muncă, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.25,0:03:50.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Poate un reprezentant al grupului să semneze aici?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Desigur.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Perfect. Mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nicio problemă.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.88,0:04:12.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Am să vă informez că s-ar putea să întâlniți niște vizitatori nedoriți pe timpul șederii voastre.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Poftim? Ce vreți să spuneți?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fantome.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.92,0:04:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ce?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,F-Fantome?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.92,0:04:24.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sunt sigură că zvonurile sunt doar rezultatul unei neînțelegeri,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.33,0:04:28.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,dar există celalaltă posibilitate, deci vă rog să țineți minte.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.08,0:04:33.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, nu! Oare vom fi în regulă? Putem lupta cu fantomele?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,N-Nu știu...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.33,0:04:40.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fantomele nu sunt reale. E doar o superstiție.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.67,0:04:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,D-Da! Și în cazul în care vom da peste una, o voi distruge cu vrăjile mele!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu-ți face griji, Lily!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, bine! Mă simt mult mai bine acum!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ar fi fost bine dacă era doar o superstiție...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Delicios! Mâncarea e așa de bună.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.29,0:05:13.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The food and amenities are wonderful, too.\NAi făcut o treabă bună găsind acest loc, Mernes.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.88,0:05:14.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.21,0:05:21.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We still haven't done anything work-related, though.\NIsn't this a learning opportunity?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.38,0:05:26.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We spent an hour discussing work!\NThat is more than enough for today.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, haideți! Asta e 100% o vacanță!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.75,0:05:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cease your prattling! We are Army leaders on\Na journey, not a vacation. My goodness.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Regină Echidna?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am going for a walk, and to purchase some snacks.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să vă însoțesc?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Da, dacă vei da peste o fantomă?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.71,0:05:48.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu se va întâmpla una ca asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, da, am uitat să vă dau ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.58,0:05:58.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Deținătoarea hanului ne-a dat aceste amulete protectoare. Luați fiecare câte una.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Amulete?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.04,0:06:01.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Astea.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cred că glumești!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.71,0:06:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She says they are ghost-dispelling charms that\Nhave been passed down here for generations.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Amulete care alungă fantomele... Ești sigură de asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am. We wouldn't want to be attacked by spirits, after all.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Asigurați-vă că le aveți la voi mereu.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bine!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.67,0:06:30.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Priviți, am patru urechi!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Așa se pare.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.38,0:06:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,These things dispel ghosts? Come on. I'm gonna pass.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see, you're going to pass, are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I suppose we should have\Nanother private drinking party, you and I!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Seeing as we seemingly need to strengthen our--
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll wear them with pride, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Haideți, puneți-le pe cap! \NE ordinul reginei noastre!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Și noi trebuie să le purtăm?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.92,0:07:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They will look flattering on the women, but can you say\Nthe same for us men?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Orders from the boss!\NKeep your head down and obey, Edvard.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is harassment.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cu toții arătați grozav!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,On that note...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.25,0:07:19.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With these, I will be fine to move about on my own.\NDo not remove the charms, now, yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.71,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Okay!\N{\rSubtitle}Yes, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna's been gone a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You think she blacked out somewhere?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.79,0:07:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Surely you jest. Echidna's tolerance\Nfor liquor is that of a bottomless pit.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.04,0:07:51.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why're there three of you, Leo?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.96,0:07:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, this one's punch-drunk on catnip juice.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.67,0:07:59.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Catnip does have that affect on canines.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go check on her.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't ditch 'cause you're losing!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not. I just won.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right on your own?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are no ghosts here.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.33,0:08:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina... Are you afraid of ghosts?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.08,0:08:22.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-of course not! I'm just being careful in\Nthe one in a million chance there's danger!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.42,0:08:26.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.88,0:08:37.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm getting pretty tired of playing Tycoon,\Nso let's take a break.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How about another drink then, Leo?\NYou still have it in you, yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.42,0:08:44.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've been doing nothing BUT drinking this whole time.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.25,0:08:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, of course! This is a special occasion,\Nwhy not share it with good friends and drink?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we shall drink until we are sated!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't drink too much, now.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nothing, just... That.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did it move?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.83,0:09:17.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-of course not! You must be seeing things!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.67,0:09:23.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Echidna? Mernes?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a look.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna and Mernes have both been absent for a\Nwhile.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I must assure their safety.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.71,0:09:44.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, you can't! Acting without permission\Nwill destroy the chain of command!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.83,0:09:50.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's tough to figure out what to do\Nwhen your boss isn't around.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hello! Anyone here?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.00,0:10:01.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know not your intentions,\Nbut you should not play pranks on--
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.88,0:10:03.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard! Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop messing around and open up!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right! You're not the type to joke around...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Th-the light!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as ghosts!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's a logical expl...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.21,0:10:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ow! What is this?! What is going on?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Where is it coming from?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina, over here!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.38,0:10:47.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's that? Is THAT... a ghost?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a rotary phone.\NAn artifact from the Mechanical Age.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Humans used these before I was born.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Allow me to silence it.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Enis la fide sol...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O wind, bring forth utter quiet!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.79,0:11:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.08,0:11:11.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,S-silence!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O wind, bring forth utter quiet!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Utter quiet!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now YOU need to be quiet!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, my spell isn't working! What do we do now?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.96,0:11:32.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll try. Silence.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo! Do something, please!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can both of you shut up?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You try, Lily!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.67,0:11:54.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, Lily, listen close. Ghosts aren't real.\NThey're just superstition.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:54.17,0:11:59.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, we have plenty of proof.\NThis was the work of a spirit.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.00,0:11:59.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:00.79,0:12:04.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I was young, we read\Na tome about ghosts and spirits.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are the strongest human monster.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.25,0:12:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can't see them and magic doesn't\Nwork on them. They're invincible.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.29,0:12:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ghosts may exist even in the Demon World!\NWe might be in trouble, Echidna!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What if one of these things attacks us?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.96,0:12:29.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not to worry! If spells don't work,\Nthen we shall punch it to death!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But how do we punch something we can't see?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Shutina.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.46,0:12:41.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are formidable enemies,\Nbut I will protect you from them!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You see?! We'll be all right.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A ghost may be among us,\Nbut Queen Echidna will keep us safe!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Help us, Echidna!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why'd you make things more complicated,\Nyou bumbling idiot succubus!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.67,0:13:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I said it! You're an adult,\Nit's your job to calm Lily down!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Generals!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.92,0:13:08.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.92,0:13:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're in danger! My spells aren't working,\Nand strange things keep happening!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've encountered strange happenings as well.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I cannot find anyone in this inn.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:21.25,0:13:25.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not the innkeep nor her staff.\NIt's as if they never existed to begin with.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,N-no...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know it's dififcult to believe, but it's likely a ghost.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where are the other three Generals?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You didn't run into them?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.75,0:13:36.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:37.29,0:13:41.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's weird. Mernes and Edvard\Nwent out looking for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, three?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily?! Hey, Lily! Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,D-did the ghost take Lily!?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is growing dire.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina! Leo! We must find our colleagues at once!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
